{"tid":514850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「守護香港」現獅子山","createTime":"2017-12-31T01:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T04:04:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"907391abffc03e3c2c451f935d58ce1f2d292d1c","tid":514850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T01:57:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171231/20260453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171231%2F20260453&d=sORSVQCKdiD82CoCnWMROW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d34c7c53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171231%2F20260453&h=9ade427a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171231/20260453</a><br />\n<br />\n「守護香港」現獅子山<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171231/large/31la4p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171231%2Flarge%2F31la4p04.jpg&h=2a17e1c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】獅子山昨日凌晨突現寫上「守護香港」的黃色直幡，惟因風勢太大被吹翻（圖），其後直幡再被消防員拆除。而「守護香港」正好是明日元旦遊行的口號。<br />\n<br />\n2017年，香港經歷特首選舉、林鄭月娥上場、4名民主派議員被DQ、社運人士因為政府覆核刑期被判入獄、立法會失守《議事規則》；到日前，全國人大常委會更以決定方式強推高鐵一地兩檢。<br />\n<br />\n就在2018年即將來臨之際，昨晨7時許，獅子山山頂突出現寫有「守護香港」的黃色直幡，由於大風緣故，直幡尾部扭成一團，未見「守護香港」以外的其他文字。消防員昨晨花約一個小時將直幡拆下。<br />\n<br />\n「守護香港」正好是明日民陣主辦的元旦遊行主題。民陣明下午發起「反閹割議會、反廿三惡法、反政治打壓、反割地兩檢、反粗暴規劃、反財團壟斷、反社會不公」遊行，遊行會於明午2時在銅鑼灣東角道集合，約2時半出發往金鐘政府總部。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張志華攝<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t譚惠珠撐人大決定等同法律陳文敏：違鄧小平依法治國<br />\n要聞 4小時前"},{"pid":"af240a1e0c9ac617a7896bae204f301236c779ac","tid":514850,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38661192ad8f5f646f0c727fdeb75811113b13bd","tid":514850,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:17:28.000Z","msg":"不如下次試下掛習近平萬歲"},{"pid":"59c68403a769fb5223aa34a35b1b526d925cff0e","tid":514850,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:35:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03233b288e7cbb8c4c117aaed972579cda788e55","tid":514850,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:37:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fe8ebf7333aedf6acf3fe0f52314e81bf657508","tid":514850,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:49:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"057e3e7cbb43b7fd64d2bbcadac3701e69a11513","tid":514850,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:53:12.000Z","msg":"三月補選<br />\n大家落力D"},{"pid":"98bbc6adb23efe085f216cd4e51a6e833294e068","tid":514850,"uid":12367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T04:04:34.000Z","msg":"咁就建左國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}